HR Director – Luxurious 5* Hotel, Dubai!
Huge opportunity for an experienced HR Director to join this stunning 5* hotel property in Dubai!
We are looking for an HR Director who has a strong hotel background and must be in a similar role in a 5* property!
It is essential that you have previous experience working in the UAE.
As HR Director, you will be responsible for all aspects of HR, Training and Development for staff members.
Working very closely with all hotel departments, you will have exceptional communication, management and organisational skills.
We are looking for a passionate, diplomatic and enthusiastic individual who is looking to join a fantastic International company who can offer amazing growth potential.
Salary Package Offered: Negotiable dependent upon experience – family status and benefits included This job was originally posted as
